 actions‚ÜźTick input;s;vis;rhobots;nIdx;targetAngle;x;y;w;h;r;spd;vr;diag;R;turnRate;margin;cx;cy;centreAngle;diff;nearWall
‚ćĚ Kamikaze: two patrol circles, charge at visible rhobots
 ‚éēIO‚Üź0
 actions‚Üź()
 s‚Üźinput.state
 vis‚Üźinput.visible
 ‚ćĚ If we see a rhobot ‚ÄĒ charge straight at it and fire
 :If 0<‚ČĘvis
     rhobots‚Üź(vis[;2]=0)‚ĆŅvis
     :If 0<‚ČĘrhobots
